--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.4.1 (2020-11-27)
E: Improve Monit configuration file

* Version 1.4.0 (2020-11-23)
F: Add support for Monit service monitoring (openssh_monitor_monit_state)

* Version 1.3.3 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 1.3.2 (2020-02-24)
E: Use Ansible module copy instead of template for static moduli file

* Version 1.3.1 (2019-10-22)
B: Disable PrintMotd on CentOS 8 by default

* Version 1.3.0 (2019-09-27)
F: Add support for CentOS 8

* Version 1.2.1 (2019-07-31)
B: Fix variable name in template

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-07-31)
F: Add support for 'AuthenticationMethods' option
F: Add support for 'ChallengeResponseAuthentication' option

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.0.1 (2019-04-15)
E: Allow additional message authentication codes (OpenSSH client)

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement

* Version 0.5.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.4.3 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.4.2 (2018-04-14)
E: Relocate 'PermitRootLogin' parameter

* Version 0.4.1 (2018-04-10)
E: Improve 'Ciphers', 'HostKeyAlgorithms', 'KexAlgorithms' and 'MACs' defaults

* Version 0.4.0 (2018-04-09)
F: Add option to define HostKeyAlgorithms

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-13)
E: Allow additional key exchange algorithms and message authentication codes

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-01-10)
E: Improve Jinja2 filters

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-05)
F: Initial release
